============================================
                 MAP-Tk
Motion-imagery Aerial Photogrammetry Toolkit
============================================

This project contains the source code for MAP-Tk.


Overview of Directories
====================

* cmake  -- contains CMake helper scripts
* doc  -- contains release notes and other documentation
* maptk  -- contains the MAP-Tk code base
* maptk/core
* maptk/core/algo
* maptk/ocv
* maptk/proj
* maptk/viscl
* maptk/vxl
* scripts
* scripts/blender
* tests
* tools
* tools/config


