Running MAP-Tk Tools
====================

Summary of MAP-Tk Tools
-----------------------

* maptk_track_featues
* maptk_bundle_adjust_tracks
* maptk_pos2krtd

Constructing Configuration Files
--------------------------------

Run tool with -o option.
Edit the config file.
Run tool again with -c config -o config
Repeat until configuration is complete
